'''Spice Mines Avenue''' was the name of a street found within the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Kessendra]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Kessel/Legends|Kessel]]. Its original designation was unknown, but the name was changed to Spice Mines Avenue at some point during the reign of [[Palpatine/Legends|Emperor Palpatine]]. At one point along the route, it intersected with [[Slave Lord Boulevard]]. [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] and [[R2-D2/Legends|R2-D2]] once passed Spice Mines Avenue on their way to rendezvous with [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] after an [[Spy/Legends|espionage]] mission at the [[Kessendra Stadium]].

